item.title: Sickness
item.description: I get sick often, and when I get sick, I get sick. I lost touch with God a lot. It sucked. How I could spend my time instead next time GET CREATIVE crochet draw paint work on website? work on some kind of low mental energy project FIND A PROJECT clean up my pinterest clean up my instagram saves (I kinda did this with covid) How I honestly spent my time with COVID (2022-06-29 to 2022-07-05) YouTube (this is just a taste of what I have been watching this week) Tiny house videos Living Big in a Tiny House Never Too Small Food Imamu’s room KWOOWK About to Eat Lisa Nguyen Jeanelleeats Christian stuff a little bit (some dating videos) Decluttering?
